comments.body:
`intlTelInputUtils` is available globally even for CommonJS users.

```typescript
import intlTelInput = require('intl-tel-input');

const input = document.querySelector('#phone');
const iti = intlTelInput(input, {
    // Asynchronously load the utils script.
    utilsScript: 'node_modules/intl-tel-input/build/js/utils.js'
});

iti.promise.then(() => {
    // `intlTelInputUtils` is available at this point.
    console.log(intlTelInputUtils.numberFormat.E164);
});
```

